Study_Name: Bainbridge Island Water Quality Monitoring Program
Study_Purpose: To design & test a comprehensive, long-term surface and nearshore water quality monitoring program.

Study_QA_Project_Plan_Description: The QAPP for the City of Bainbridge Island Water Quality Monitoring Program summarizes the project background, details the data quality objectives, establishes the organization, and presents the quality assurance (QA) requirements and quality control (QC).
